These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
Hobby: reading, filmmaking
Cigar: game, ritmeester
1. Hobby:filmmaking is on the left or right of Hobby:reading##3
2. Cigar:ritmeester is on the right of Hobby:filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | reading |
| Cigar       | game | ritmeester |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
Hobby: board-games, collecting
Color: blood-red, coral
1. Color:coral is on the left or right of Hobby:collecting##3
2. Hobby:collecting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Hobby   | board-games | collecting |
| Color      | coral     | blood-red  |

 #################################
 
